quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,187,"On dagnanaama he jemma koorka yiidugol e rew…ďe mon …ďen. Ko …ďe koltu mo'on ko on koltu ma…ď…ďe. Alla anndii wonde on laatinoke jaŇčfotoo…ďe koye mon, o Ja…ďanii on tuubuubuyee o Ya'fiima on.Jooni noon,soccondiree he ma…ď…ďe …óa…ď…ďon ko Alla winndani on.√Ďaamee yaron haa gaarawol danewol ngol …ďaŇčngirana on …ďalewol ngol ka peeral, refti timminiron koorka kan jemma. Wata on soccondir e ma…ď…ďe hara ko on ufnii…ďe ka juulir…óe.∆äum ko keeri Allah, wata on …ďa…óto …ói.Ko wano nii Alla …ďaŇčnginiraŇčta yim…ďe …ďen aayeeje makko …óen, bela jo'o …ďe wona reentii…ďe."
  2,188,"Wata on √Īaamir jawle (jaw…óeele ) mon …óen hakkunde mon he mehre, werloron …óe e √Īaawoo…ďe …ďen fii yo fedde goo √Īaamira e jawle yim…ďe …ďen bakkaatu, hara hi…óon nganndi."
  2,189,"Hi…ďe naamno maa fii daror…óe lebbi, wi'u: "∆äin ko tumaaji yim…ďe e fii hajju".Dewal ngal wonaali nde naatirto cuu…ói …óin immorde ka babbe (dame) majji, si ko woni dewal ngal: ko on (oon) gom…óu…óo.Ngardee cuu…ói …óin ka dame majji.Hulon Allah,belaj joo male-…óon."
  2,190,"Ha…ďee fii laawol Alla ngol …ďen ha…ďatoo…ďe on, wata too√Īee. Pellet, Alla yi…óaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen."